{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21083.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"静海木叶","textCenter":"『烹饪教室开课通知』，@开办学习班的餐厅是……","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":400}],"textCenter":"[chara:302601:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]『胡桃西餐厅』，@是胡桃西餐厅！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302601}],"textCenter":"是神滨最有名的餐厅啊。"},{"chara":[{"id":302601,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"静海木叶","nameRight":"游佐叶月","textRight":"以前我去那里参加过女生聚会，@那里的东西好吃到让人流泪……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"叶月！你终于恢复意识了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601}],"textLeft":"不过……叶月，菖蒲，@你们怎么想？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"即使我熟读这本书，@烹饪技术也没有得到改善……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601}],"textLeft":"参加烹饪教室，@就能做好菜了吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"三栗菖蒲","textRight":"难得@你这么没自信啊，木叶！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"诶？@[chara:302601:lipSynch_0][wait:0.5][chara:302601:cheek_0][chara:302601:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json][chara:302601:lipSynch_1]这个……我当然会没自信啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601}],"textLeft":"我那么努力学习，@拼尽全力……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"做出的饭菜却还是@一点进步也没有啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601}],"textLeft":"[chara:302601:effect_emotion_sad_0][se:7224_fall_into]我原以为至少不至于@让吃下去的人昏迷呢……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"游佐叶月","textRight":"不过，能让胡桃西餐厅的人教你@也很厉害了哦！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302701}],"textRight":"这种机会@可不常有。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":1}],"textRight":"能当面看着老师做菜，@并请教他烹饪方法……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302701}],"textRight":"做错的时候，还可以@当场请教专家！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":200}],"textRight":"如果木叶你@真的无论如何，"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302701}],"textRight":"都想学会@烹饪的话……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302701,"motion":100}],"textRight":"那就要尽一切努力去尝试！@不是吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"（而且，在烹饪教室，@试吃的人就不是我们了！）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"是啊……我无论如何@都想学好烹饪。","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302601}],"textLeft":"无论用怎样的手段，@花费多少时间……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"我都必须要做出@美味的饭菜才行。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302601}],"textLeft":"这不仅关系到@我们的支出……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"同时也是@我与叶月、菖蒲的约定嘛。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"三栗菖蒲","textRight":"呃、嗯……@我们有约定过吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":100}],"textRight":"不过，我觉得@烹饪教室这主意不错！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":302801,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"（这样我就@不用再试吃了。）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"谢谢你们……","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"我要去参加@这个烹饪教室！"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302601,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3026_00_03","textHome":"调味料的用法？嗯……无可奉告。"}],"nameCenter":"静海木叶","textCenter":"烹饪的基本原则？@嗯……无可奉告。","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302601,"motion":100}]},{"chara":[{"id":302601}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}